<L>__{exterior waterfront night}
<B>__{deserted. a long shadow of a man stretches out across the}
<A>__{dock. it is peter, walking leisurely from the waterfront}
<B>__{drive toward the huge waterhouse at the end of the dock. he steps into the deep shadows and seems to vanish.}
